data.description: Beautifully end unit that is bright and airy!  Many  updates, including New windows, bathroom, custom tile work, granite countertops, SS appliances, hardwood floor.  Two story, cathedral ceiling in the living room with sky-high windows. Huge master suite fit for a King and Queen w/vaulted ceilings, recessed lights in whole house, whirlpool & separate shower.Convenient to downtown Bartlett, the train station, Route 20, and the Elgin-O'Hare Expressway, making your daily commute and access to tons of shopping
